title: Genuine Notre Dame custom made pen From Bleacher wood with COA
description: This pen is custom hand turned by me (Bill Holland) in my home studio. This is an actual piece of the seat from the Notre Dame Bleacher seat, complete with COA showing where the wood was acquired as well as a small piece of wood with the original paint on it. This pen is a VERY RARE and unique piece of Fighting Irish history. It is carefully hand turned on my lathe & with a 15 step process sanded & polished to 12,000 grit to a glass like finish. It is a unique one of a kind gift that you will not see another like it. Pens make the perfect gift for that special person who has everything. Chances are they do not have a high end handcrafted exotic pen. This is a high quality pen & will make a great first impression. this is a great item for a professional type person like a doctor, lawyer or someone who does a lot of writing. This pen has a very smooth mechanism & is built with quality Chrome plated components made to last a lifetime. I can also build a pen with the wood or burl of your choosing. I have some customers who request I use wood with a story or meaning. I have also made pens from salvage materials. I also have woods from most other stadiums either on hand or can be acquired and made into pen. Message me for a list of all my available woods. NC Wood Art only uses the finest and rarest of exotic woods and burls for the pieces offered and they make wonderful gifts for any occasion. Here is my current inventory of Whiskey, bourbon and wine barrel blanks. I can make pen, key ring, toothpick holder or ceiling fan pulls.

title: Ruthven Scottish Clan Crest Celtic Cross Pendant
description: ALL CLANS ARE AVAILABLE.

This beautiful sterling silver or gold pendant combines an intricate Celtic cross background with your Clan crest mounted in the center. The Clan crest is exquisitely handcrafted and is 11/16" (19.5 mm) in diameter while the very detailed Celtic cross is 1-3/16" (30mm) square. The sterling silver pendant includes an 18" sterling silver box link chain. In gold a chain is available at an extra charge. Please inquire. This piece is crafted in high quality sterling silver, 10K and 14K yellow or white gold.
A wonderful way to display your proud Scottish Clan heritage.

The Clan crest is surrounded by a detailed belt and buckle design upon which is inscribed your Clan motto in raised relief lettering. In ancient times, the chief of the Clan presented to his Clansmen his crest for them to wear as a symbol of their loyalty and Clan affiliation.  We make our Clan designs by the “lost wax casting” process, which allows us to carve our master designs deeper in wax than would be possible with simple metal engraving. Each piece is painstakingly made by hand and the difference in the quality of design is significant. These are the finest detailed Clan crests available in the world! Our company has been in the Scottish Clan crest business for over forty one years. We are now making Clan and other Scottish jewellery for the children and grandchildren of our original customers!.
Alba gu brath!
